---

<MainLayout
  title="Commercial Metal Roofing in Temple, Killeen & Central Texas | Lone Ranger Roofing"
  description="Lone Ranger Roofing installs commercial metal roofing across Temple, Killeen, and Central Texas. Standing seam, R-panel, on-site fabrication. Built to last 40-70 years. Free commercial estimate."
  darkHero={true}
>

  <!-- ===================== HERO ===================== -->
  <section class="relative min-h-[65vh] flex items-center bg-brand-900 overflow-hidden -mt-28">
    <div class="absolute inset-0">
      <img
        src="/commercial-roofing-hero.webp"
        alt="Commercial metal roofing installation — Temple and Killeen TX"
        class="w-full h-full object-cover"
      />
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-brand-900 via-brand-900/85 to-brand-900/30"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="relative z-10 container mx-auto px-4 pt-20 pb-28">
      <div class="max-w-2xl">
        <p class="text-gold-400 font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">Commercial Roofing</p>
        <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-black text-white leading-tight mb-6">
          Commercial Metal Roofing in Temple, Killeen &amp; Central Texas
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-200 leading-relaxed mb-8">
          The longest-lasting commercial roof you can put on a building. On-site fabrication, no supplier delays.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
          <a href="/contact" class="bg-accent-600 hover:bg-accent-700 text-white font-black px-8 py-4 rounded-lg text-sm uppercase tracking-wide transition-colors text-center shadow-lg">
            Get a Free Commercial Estimate
          </a>
          <a href="tel:+12543001413" class="border-2 border-white/50 hover:border-white text-white font-bold px-8 py-4 rounded-lg text-sm uppercase tracking-wide transition-colors text-center hover:bg-white/10">
            Call (254) 300-1413
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-x-6 gap-y-3 mt-10">
          {[
            'On-Site Fabrication Machine',
            'Material + Labor Warranty',
            'Financing Available',
          ].map(t => (
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-gray-300 text-sm">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-gold-400 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
              </svg>
              {t}
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===================== KEEPING YOUR DOORS OPEN ===================== -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white overflow-hidden">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center max-w-6xl mx-auto">

        <div>
          <p class="text-accent-600 font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">KEEPING YOUR DOORS OPEN</p>
          <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-black text-brand-900 mb-6">
            A New Roof Shouldn't Mean Closed Signs
          </h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Every hour your building's shut down for roof work is money out of your pocket. We get that. So we don't plan commercial jobs around our convenience — we plan them around yours.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            That means scheduling the loud, disruptive parts during off-hours when we can, keeping work zones tight so entrances and parking stay open, and putting one project lead on-site who actually knows what's happening — not a rotating cast of guys you have to re-explain things to. For property owners and managers in Temple, Killeen, Belton, Waco, and across DFW, that's the difference between a roof project and a business interruption.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="relative">
          <img
            src="/commercial-roofing1.webp"
            alt="Lone Ranger Roofing commercial roofing project in progress"
            class="w-full h-[480px] object-cover rounded-2xl shadow-xl"
          />
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===================== METAL SYSTEMS ===================== -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-6xl">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <p class="text-accent-600 font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">SYSTEMS WE INSTALL</p>
        <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-black text-brand-900 mb-4">
          Commercial Metal Roofing Systems We Install
        </h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
          Lone Ranger Roofing installs all major commercial metal roofing systems across Temple, Killeen, Belton, Waco, and the DFW metro. We'll recommend the right system based on your building type, budget, and performance requirements.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-3 gap-5">
        {metalSystems.map(item => (
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-7 shadow-sm border border-gray-100 flex flex-col gap-4">
            <div class="w-11 h-11 rounded-xl bg-accent-600/10 text-accent-600 flex items-center justify-center" set:html={item.icon} />
            <h3 class="font-black text-brand-900 text-lg">{item.title}</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">{item.body}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===================== WHY COMMERCIAL METAL ===================== -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-6xl">
      <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-10 items-center mb-14">
        <div class="lg:w-1/2">
          <p class="text-accent-600 font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">WHY METAL FOR COMMERCIAL</p>
          <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-black text-brand-900 mb-4">
            Why Commercial Property Owners in Central Texas Are Moving to Metal
          </h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            Commercial roofs get used hard. HVAC foot traffic, rooftop equipment, Texas hail, and decade after decade of UV exposure take a toll on systems that weren't built to last. Metal roofing outlasts every alternative — and the long-term math almost always favors it.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="lg:w-1/2 grid grid-cols-2 gap-3">
          <img src="/commercial-roofing2.webp" alt="Commercial metal roof installation Central Texas" loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="w-full h-40 object-cover rounded-xl shadow-md" />
          <img src="/commercial-roofing3.webp" alt="Commercial standing seam metal roofing" loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="w-full h-40 object-cover rounded-xl shadow-md mt-6" />
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-5">
        {whyMetalCards.map(item => (
          <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-7 border border-gray-100 flex flex-col gap-4">
            <div class="w-11 h-11 rounded-xl bg-accent-600/10 text-accent-600 flex items-center justify-center" set:html={item.icon} />
            <h3 class="font-black text-brand-900 text-lg">{item.title}</h3>
